document_data.name: Talisovanar Fellbranch
document_data.mainbody: '''Talisovanar "Tally" Fellbranch''' ({{Pronounce|tal|iss|AWL|van|ar|refs=}}) was a [[half-elf]] carpenter and woodcarver in [[Waterdeep]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Activities: Tally managed the [[Bent Nail]] shop on [[Trollskull Alley]] in the [[Waterdeep/North Ward|North Ward]].

Relationships.Melannor: Tally was brother to [[Melannor Fellbranch]].<ref>{{Cite web | title=Waterdeep: Dragon Heist's Factions are Perfect for Beginner and Veteran DMs| publisher=D&D Beyond | date=2018-09-12 | work= | url=https://www.dndbeyond.com/posts/317-waterdeep-dragon-heists-factions-are-perfect-for| accessdate=2019-02-13 | editor=[[James Haeck]] }}
